{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"42278f99c5","title":"给朱绍良\"的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bd2c94abe0","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":8,"articleId":"42278f99c5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"adc59903be","type":"paragraph","text":"给朱绍良\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5"},{"id":"a9dcfc94be","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年9月8日）绍良先生","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5"},{"id":"aee209f89a","type":"paragraph","text":"十年酷战，随处与先生相遇，可谓大有缘笑！然鹤蚌相持，渔人同于其侧，为鹤蚌者不亦危乎？付上共产党致国民党书，为国家民族谋，亦为先生谋也。两党两军之间，无胶固不解之兔，有同舟共济之责。抛嫌释织，以对付共同之敌，天下后世颂先生为民族英雄，点不愈于胡宗南君所谓“无期徒刑”乎？天“丽”非特无期徒刑也，且是一种死刑。非日红军宣告先生们之死刑也，日本帝国主义实宣告之，非特宣告国人某一部分于死刑，实欲举全民族而宣告之，鸣呼危笑！先生而同意统一战线，则部人竭诚以迎。惟事宜急办，迁延则利在长驱而入之寇。尚祈致意蒋先生回，立即决策，国事犹可为也。书不尽意。顺颂勋祺！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5"},{"id":"f16c3c40c6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东启","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5"},{"id":"3ad5212e4b","type":"paragraph","text":"九月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5"},{"id":"4884b11db7","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]朱绍良（1891—1963），原籍江苏武进，当时任国民党政府驻甘绥靖公署主任。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5"},{"id":"3bfd685816","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]胡宗南（1896—1962），浙江孝丰（今并入安吉）人，当时任国民党军第一军军长，在陕北进攻红军。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5"},{"id":"bc09bd8aa9","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]指蒋介石。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5"}],"page":{"id":"24b6a12673","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"42278f99c5","start":115,"end":115}}}},"__N_SSG":true}